flowchart TD
    E["GE_COMMANDS entry\n{ path, cli, risk, requirements, argv }"] --> CLI["ge CLI\nsame argv, same core"]
    E --> RT["console route\ncommandForRoute() → job sentinel"]
    RT --> P{"preflight\ncommandDoctor(requirements)"}
